Erudites are known more for their brain power than for their muscle-power, so it is unsurprising that what little cultural smithing they perform is geared towards making stronger threads for their cultural tailoring.<p>
As with all cultural tradeskills, these combines are race-restricted. They must be performed by real erudites, using their cultural forge. Illusions will not fool this, or any other cultural tradeskill container.<br><div align="right">Last Modified By: Niami Denmother&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<br>

		Last Modified on: 2003-05-19 06:04:01&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</i></div><br>
